Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.50,0:00:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經結束了 死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.91,0:00:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要結束的 是你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.14,0:00:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎你 Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.15,0:00:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.27,0:01:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.88,0:01:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能動？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.40,0:01:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.83,0:01:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該已經穿透脊椎讓她暈過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.22,0:01:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是Zero啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.13,0:01:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.14,0:01:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就再插狠點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.74,0:01:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將你體內的中心所在之物…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.71,0:02:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒人聯絡我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.58,0:02:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.07,0:02:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條隧道 一直通到哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.10,0:02:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽繪理說 前面貌似有個很大的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.12,0:02:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在聽她說詳情之前 通信機就被打爛了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.63,0:02:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.07,0:03:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:39.31,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}わたしはもっと がんばれるって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:39.31,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}「我會更加努力」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.48,0:03:42.50,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}約束した きみと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.48,0:03:42.50,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}曾向你如此許諾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:46.68,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}隠しごとは キライだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:46.68,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}雖然討厭隱瞞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.90,0:03:50.32,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}痛みはみせないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.90,0:03:50.32,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}但不會給你看到我的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.02,0:03:54.30,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}強く生きるために
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.02,0:03:54.30,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}為了堅強地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:03:58.00,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}つくられたカラダを
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:03:58.00,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}上天賜予的這副軀體
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:04:03.91,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}かわいいと ほめてほしい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:04:03.91,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}只望你能讚美一句可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:08.59,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}月がにじむ 夜空は群青
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:08.59,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}月光朦朧 夜空群青
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.80,0:04:12.80,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}完璧な世界 信じてる Blue sky
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.80,0:04:12.80,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}是相信這完美世界的藍天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:18.89,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}流星よ 明日へ つれていって
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:18.89,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}流星啊 請帶我去往明日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.91,0:04:23.33,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}メカニズムは 読めない 純情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.91,0:04:23.33,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}機械結構是無法解讀的純情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.54,0:04:27.19,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}君と芽生えた 友情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.54,0:04:27.19,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}與你萌生的友情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.25,0:04:30.76,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}涙 瞳は 強情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.25,0:04:30.76,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}眼中的淚水 流露出倔強
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.94,0:04:34.39,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}確信のほうへ シフト決めた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.94,0:04:34.39,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}向著自己堅信的方向轉移
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:36.77,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}ベクトルはブレない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:36.77,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}方向不會動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:38.66,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}We are flying kids
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:38.66,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}We are flying kids
