Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.61,0:05:02.00,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Flight 03 「Zero」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那…是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.17,0:05:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侵蝕？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.83,0:05:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.13,0:05:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香奈 凜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.87,0:05:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你是什麼人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.13,0:05:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都休想壞我們的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.83,0:05:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.83,0:05:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空手就彈開了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.07,0:06:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓船起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.69,0:06:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要留在這顆星球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.82,0:06:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢復不了原狀了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她再繼續攻擊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Zero」？那是指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.02,0:06:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是所謂的真核物質
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們的原生體
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到竟然在這顆星球上存活至今
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是同伴了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.26,0:07:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知是否是那知性體的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.03,0:07:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero往顯著扭曲的方向得到了進化
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不再跟我們是同種了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是敵人咯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果硬要分類的話 這話是沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破壞？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.71,0:07:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 馬上傳達給她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.01,0:08:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓來的女孩都在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.63,0:08:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.51,0:08:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們倆都被幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.21,0:08:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的是那些女孩子啊 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.57,0:08:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.31,0:08:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,資料已經採集完了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她專注於那邊 就不會過來礙我們的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.76,0:09:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.21,0:09:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍華
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花憐學姐 理沙子老師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.28,0:09:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被抓走的女孩子都在裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.14,0:09:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.32,0:09:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 不知道怎麼打開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.10,0:09:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門就是不開呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.66,0:09:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個女孩不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.46,0:09:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 原來你被插了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦啊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.19,0:10:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.03,0:10:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空軍戰機 已經準備好起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.59,0:10:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛到目標上空要多久時間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到達目標的預定時刻為 1500
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計趕不上目標發射呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果它要飛去衛星軌道的話 肯定會往東邊上升
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.95,0:10:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航空母艦什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.76,0:10:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經往目標的預測路徑進發
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.81,0:10:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.63,0:11:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(戰鷹1號 準備滑行)\NEagle 1 Clear for Taxi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.94,0:11:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(23號跑道)\NRunway 23
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(收到 準備滑行)\NRoger Clear for Taxi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.63,0:11:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(23號跑道)\NRunway 23
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從時鐘塔上方搬到這種地方啊
